abstract: Writers across the political spectrum responded to the public release of the special counsel’s report.
snippet: Writers across the political spectrum responded to the public release of the special counsel’s report.
lead_paragraph: The political news cycle is fast, and keeping up can be overwhelming. Trying to find differing perspectives worth your time is even harder. That’s why we have scoured the internet for writing from across the political spectrum that you might not have seen.

headline_main: DealBook Briefing: Business Heads Back to Saudi Arabia

abstract: The choice of Ms. Crowley for the Treasury’s top communications role comes about two years after she withdrew as a candidate for other administration jobs in the face of plagiarism accusations.
snippet: The choice of Ms. Crowley for the Treasury’s top communications role comes about two years after she withdrew as a candidate for other administration jobs in the face of plagiarism accusations.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin plans to hire Monica Crowley, a longtime Fox News commentator, as his top communications official, according to a person familiar with the matter.

abstract: Concern about mass shootings has lifted spending on studies and attracted a new generation of researchers.
snippet: Concern about mass shootings has lifted spending on studies and attracted a new generation of researchers.
lead_paragraph: In 1996, the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention stopped funding research into the causes of gun violence. And for decades the field suffered from neglect: low funding and a corresponding limited interest in academia.

abstract: Political journalists gathered in Chicago to discuss the mistakes of 2016 and how to avoid them the next time around.
snippet: Political journalists gathered in Chicago to discuss the mistakes of 2016 and how to avoid them the next time around.
lead_paragraph: CHICAGO — Journalists have no idea how the 2020 election will play out. And that’s a good thing.

headline_main: DealBook Briefing: Billionaires Pledge Hundreds of Millions to Save Notre-Dame

abstract: Members of the party establishment who oppose Bernie Sanders have had discussions about how to handle his candidacy, while others warn of a schism within the party.
snippet: Members of the party establishment who oppose Bernie Sanders have had discussions about how to handle his candidacy, while others warn of a schism within the party.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — When Leah Daughtry, a former Democratic Party official, addressed a closed-door gathering of about 100 wealthy liberal donors in San Francisco last month, all it took was a review of the 2020 primary rules to throw a scare in them.

abstract: The museum said that it was “deeply concerned” about renting the space for an event to honor someone whose environmental policies had been widely criticized.
snippet: The museum said that it was “deeply concerned” about renting the space for an event to honor someone whose environmental policies had been widely criticized.
lead_paragraph: The American Museum of Natural History said Monday that it would no longer host an event at the museum by an outside organization that was to have honored President Jair Bolsonaro of Brazil, whose environmental policies have come under fire.

abstract: The museum said it was “deeply concerned” that the event it is hosting will honor Brazil’s president, whose environmental policies have drawn criticism.
snippet: The museum said it was “deeply concerned” that the event it is hosting will honor Brazil’s president, whose environmental policies have drawn criticism.
lead_paragraph: The American Museum of Natural History says it is exploring its options after discovering that the honoree at a gala to which it rented space next month will be President Jair Bolsonaro of Brazil, whose environmental policies have come under fire.
